{"tid":2334524,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"變種武漢肺炎 恐已在法國傳播","createTime":"2020-12-21T08:27:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T09:57:11.000Z","uid":13663,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"93f92b4600a2fcda9dfba48ab2ad665edf902a70","tid":2334524,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T08:27:54.000Z","msg":"法國衛生部長維宏21日接受歐洲1台廣播電台訪問時說，雖然法國還未在檢測中發現變種新冠病毒，但它可能已在法國傳播。<br />\n<br />\n維宏說：「這種病毒完全有可能在法國散播。」<br />\n<br />\n變種新冠病毒的傳染力似乎增加七成，已有多國暫時禁止自英國啟程的飛機和旅客入境。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/5109905\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F5109905&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzAsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=d4cc7963\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/5109905</a>"},{"pid":"863b85b23d3ad239b894e1cde656b8efc5ab5f6f","tid":2334524,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T08:28:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UV5Xwy1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUV5Xwy1.jpg&h=107c3c7d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UiFAid2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUiFAid2.jpg&h=5c7dbeb3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mqqwA0H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmqqwA0H.png&h=b9a1194a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n封唔封法國呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"804a5d2bd271c9640258de133184c2c698ece7e0","tid":2334524,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T08:31:31.000Z","msg":"法國衛生部長：新冠病毒疫苗應該可以對抗新毒株<br />\n新聞 | 22分鐘以前 | 由 FXStreet團隊<br />\n<br />\n法國衛生部長奧利維爾&middot;韋蘭（Olivier Veran）週一在接受歐洲一號電台採訪時表示，目前的冠狀病毒疫苗有望有效對抗在英國發現的新病毒株。<br />\n<br />\n他說：&ldquo;理論上，沒有理由認為疫苗不應該有效。 &rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n此前，英國首相鮑里斯&bull;約翰遜（Boris Johnson）在英國實施了有效的封鎖措施，並取消了在聖誕節期間放鬆管制的計劃，因為新毒株的傳染率比原來的高出70 %。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />驚閪咩"},{"pid":"f18e703b5b5bdf422edf3a48f6b3ae3350c4b3ce","tid":2334524,"uid":123738,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T08:47:10.000Z","msg":"支那武漢肺炎變左種，都係屬於支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n沒有野可以逃出支那控制"},{"pid":"7e59ef428671905a578a46355af3d195caab7869","tid":2334524,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T08:50:34.000Z","msg":"幾時傳番去發源地支那武漢"},{"pid":"df4363169b3b689261ed3af62e1fc33129282e29","tid":2334524,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T08:51:04.000Z","msg":"港共要封埋法國了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eafb71191de2af1eb0344c558658be923d56fd09","tid":2334524,"uid":331590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T08:52:15.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">陳肇始以污名化英國為目的既變種武肺病毒<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"e400695446e355dff5deb3a7bab06fe9b6dcdfcd","tid":2334524,"uid":185656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f18e703b5b5bdf422edf3a48f6b3ae3350c4b3ce","tid":2334524,"uid":123738,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T08:47:10.000Z","msg":"支那武漢肺炎變左種，都係屬於支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n沒有野可以逃出支那控制"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T08:53:08.000Z","msg":"它首先是支那公民<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd460f5b4f2f2d02bac103ba3dd3fd30b65a3e64","tid":2334524,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df4363169b3b689261ed3af62e1fc33129282e29","